  "texts": [
    "These articles were manually curated based on relevance, number of citations, and the impact factor of the published journal.",
    "However, the relevance of the article to the task at hand was prioritized over other criteria.",
    "We only included peer-reviewed articles in this step to ensure scientific accountability.",
    "An additional technical benefit is the lower recall within the RAG framework.",
    "The references to the articles used in this work can be found in the XpertAI GitHub repository."
